{"tid":2004932,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手睇下呢個位可唔可以右轉？","createTime":"2020-05-06T19:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T00:53:11.000Z","uid":296769,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4a68cbf052cc2db0a4957dd2bafcbc87321d15ea","tid":2004932,"uid":296769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqwbuVt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqwbuVt.jpg&h=77f0e220&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5CFofu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5CFofu.jpg&h=4e434905&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想問上面個位可唔可以右轉？無不可右轉牌，不過地下又雙白線</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ytNNNHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FytNNNHO.jpg&h=2322fe85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外呢個位都想知可唔可右轉？又係無不可右轉牌，不過地下雙白線</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6b31c98995b6129456a9d9bcddaf0c0dbe95686c","tid":2004932,"uid":258899,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"香港道路規則 - 冷智識 - 雙白線可右轉<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎，好多人都以為雙白線不準右轉，甚至乎比差佬抄過牌。<br />\n其實雙白線係可以右轉。但不準掉頭。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛人士可越過雙白綫向右轉入／轉出道路或樓宇<br />\n<br />\n例如停車場出入口，對開是雙白線，同樣是可轉右駛入或駛出。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源： 運輸署網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_5_for_all_drivers%2Fdouble_white_lines_%2Findex.html%23&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e48d8664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#</a>"},{"pid":"a9e7d2c18ae330814a00ff0cfa9ca80b4ec0c8e8","tid":2004932,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b31c98995b6129456a9d9bcddaf0c0dbe95686c","tid":2004932,"uid":258899,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"香港道路規則 - 冷智識 - 雙白線可右轉<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎，好多人都以為雙白線不準右轉，甚至乎比差佬抄過牌。<br />\n其實雙白線係可以右轉。但不準掉頭。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛人士可越過雙白綫向右轉入／轉出道路或樓宇<br />\n<br />\n例如停車場出入口，對開是雙白線，同樣是可轉右駛入或駛出。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源： 運輸署網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_5_for_all_drivers%2Fdouble_white_lines_%2Findex.html%23&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e48d8664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ee333b1fea7d43601f87f6e8369e4aea6c3b56","tid":2004932,"uid":29131,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港道路規則 - 冷智識 - 雙白線可右轉<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎，好多人都以為雙白線不準右轉，甚<span style=\"color: red;\">至乎比差佬抄過牌。</span><br />\n其實雙白線係可以右轉。但不準掉頭。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛人士可越過雙白綫向右轉入／轉出道路或樓宇<br />\n<br />\n例如停車場出入口，對開是雙白線，同樣是可轉右駛入或駛出。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源： 運輸署網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_5_for_all_drivers%2Fdouble_white_lines_%2Findex.html%23&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e48d8664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97c13bf9ffeea10481c8b7eb18dbbd71e338d71","tid":2004932,"uid":215311,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:23:15.000Z","msg":"其實都唔算冷知識<br />\n除非有不準轉右牌<br />\n否則轉右係無問題既"},{"pid":"1f3819127a429a732c2a9dd1fba4d59050177304","tid":2004932,"uid":120440,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:27:25.000Z","msg":"可以右轉<br />\n佢無不準右轉就可以轉<br />\n<br />\n你當個情況就好似你要入啲屋苑又或者停車場咁，打燈照轉"},{"pid":"cfc64665ae2923bc00e5d9fb6a2ad713717fce8d","tid":2004932,"uid":158601,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdYUvp3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdYUvp3.png&h=70433be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個位點睇？"},{"pid":"ff30bf6b0a7d8c5cdf729519595722d801ae71ce","tid":2004932,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"u turn就唔得<br />\n無指明既話轉右或入停車場／大廈／路口就可以"},{"pid":"be406c5aefcb13aec5220b6714ead652655f45b6","tid":2004932,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"6b31c98995b6129456a9d9bcddaf0c0dbe95686c","tid":2004932,"uid":258899,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"香港道路規則 - 冷智識 - 雙白線可右轉<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎，好多人都以為雙白線不準右轉，甚至乎比差佬抄過牌。<br />\n其實雙白線係可以右轉。但不準掉頭。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛人士可越過雙白綫向右轉入／轉出道路或樓宇<br />\n<br />\n例如停車場出入口，對開是雙白線，同樣是可轉右駛入或駛出。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源： 運輸署網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/double_white_lines_/index.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_5_for_all_drivers%2Fdouble_white_lines_%2Findex.html%23&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e48d86